        "subject": "[URGENT] Reallocation Approval Required",
        "html": "=<h3>[URGENT] Mutual Fund Reallocation Approval Required</h3>\n<p>A high-risk mutual fund reallocation has been proposed by the AI Analyst pipeline and requires human sign-off.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Fund Name:</strong> {{ $node[\"When Executed by Another Workflow\"].json.scheme_name }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Proposed Reallocation Weight:</strong> {{ $node[\"When Executed by Another Workflow\"].json.reallocation_pct }}%</li>\n  <li><strong>Fund Standard Deviation (Volatility):</strong> {{ $node[\"When Executed by Another Workflow\"].json.std_dev }}%</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please review and choose an action below:</p>\n<a href=\"{{ $execution.resumeUrl }}?action=approve\" style=\"background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block;\">Approve Reallocation</a>\n<a href=\"{{ $execution.resumeUrl }}?action=reject\" style=\"background-color: #f44336; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;\">Reject Reallocation</a>",
        "options": {}
